OL,3,CHow will ban on phones in schools
OL,4,Cwork? Your questions answered
OL,6,FPhones will be banned in all of
OL,7,FEngland's schools when pupils return
OL,8,Ffrom the summer holidays in September,
OL,9,Fin an attempt to keep them focused and
OL,10,Fcut distractions.
OL,12,FBut the new law says schools should
OL,13,Fdecide how to enforce the rule
OL,14,Fthemselves, meaning a mixed picture
OL,15,Facross the country.
OL,17,FRevealing the confusion felt by some,
OL,18,Fwere the thousands of questions sent
OL,19,Fin to the Smartphone Free Childhood
OL,20,F(SFC) group by parents and teachers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
