OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784301514
OL,3,CHow will ban on phones in schools
OL,4,Cwork? Your questions answered
OL,6,FTo clear up some of that confusion, I
OL,7,Fsat down with Schools Minister Olivia
OL,8,FBailey MP, asking her questions from
OL,9,Fparents and teachers, as well as some
OL,10,Fof my own.
OL,12,FWatch Schools Minister Olivia Bailey
OL,13,Fanswers questions about ban on phones
OL,14,Fin school:
OL,16,FThe Smartphone Free Childhood group
OL,17,Fsaid it welcomes the ban on phones in
OL,18,Fschools but wants the government to go
OL,19,Ffurther, warning it's "it's not a
OL,20,Fsilver bullet".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
