OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784301514
OL,3,CHow will ban on phones in schools
OL,4,Cwork? Your questions answered
OL,6,F"Parents and teachers right across our
OL,7,Fcommunity really welcome the updated
OL,8,Fguidance and putting it on a statutory
OL,9,Ffooting," said Fiona Beresford, the
OL,10,Fprogramme director of Smartphone Free
OL,11,FChildhood's schools network.
OL,13,F"We appreciate that this isn't a
OL,14,Fsilver bullet, but it is one lever and
OL,15,Fpart of a bigger picture that can help
OL,16,Fsupport and encourage children and
OL,17,Fgive children their their childhoods
OL,18,Fback."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
