OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784301514
OL,3,CHow will ban on phones in schools
OL,4,Cwork? Your questions answered
OL,6,FWith schools allowed to choose their
OL,7,Fown enforcement strategies, some are
OL,8,Fopting to force phones into lockers or
OL,9,Fsealed pouches, while others simply
OL,10,Ftell pupils to keep devices in their
OL,11,Fbags.
OL,13,FAsked if the law should be
OL,14,Fstrengthened, Ms Beresford said: "The
OL,15,Fmost transformative policies in
OL,16,Fschools are those truly smartphone
OL,17,Ffree policies that encourage that
OL,18,Fbroader cultural change and start to
OL,19,Fshift the norm towards delaying
OL,20,Fownership of smartphones.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
